        <mxCell id="s5_why" value="&lt;b&gt;Why it matters:&lt;/b&gt; Raw angle data is noisy. Low-pass filters smooth the curve; peak detection finds rep tops/bottoms; min/max gives ROM per rep." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f9f9f9;strokeColor=#ccc;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
